Deployment:
---------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
The steps to deploy the war file are as follows:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

-----
prod
-----
1) ftp the proper war file to your desktop in binary mode
2) prod: http://chi1pas1.uscc.com:8082 (using IE) 
3) click on "Tomcat Manager", login as sysmgr with password cares123
4) Find the /calldump or /calldump_test Application and hit "Undeploy"
5) Go to "WAR file to deploy" section, hit BROWSE button and locate WAR file
6) hit "Deploy" button


-----
